{"type":"message","id":"d6d76090","parentId":"985c562f","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:12:24.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have collected a comprehensive list of skills. Now let me organize them and create a report for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搜索完成，我来整理一份适合情报研究员的能力提升技能清单："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-0c6005f8a92240e4950c5b1743b02a29","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 情报研究员技能推荐清单\n\n搜索时间：2026-03-06\n来源：ClawHub (skills.sh)\n\n---\n\n## 一、核心能力提升技能（强烈推荐）\n\n### 1. 深度研究能力\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **tavily-ai/skills@research** | 3.6K | `npx skills add tavily-ai/skills@research` |\n| **199-biotechnologies/claude-deep-research-skill@deep-research** | 1.4K | `npx skills add 199-biotechnologies/claude-deep-research-skill@deep-research` |\n| **shubhamsaboo/awesome-llm-apps@deep-research** | 1.1K | `npx skills add shubhamsaboo/awesome-llm-apps@deep-research` |\n| **shubhamsaboo/awesome-llm-apps@academic-researcher** | 1.2K | `npx skills add shubhamsaboo/awesome-llm-apps@academic-researcher` |\n\n**推荐理由**：Tavily是AI优化的搜索API，research技能专为深度调研设计，适合做行业分析和竞品研究。\n\n### 2. 网页爬取能力\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **jamditis/claude-skills-journalism@web-scraping** | 805 | `npx skills add jamditis/claude-skills-journalism@web-scraping` |\n| **mindrally/skills@web-scraping** | 378 | `npx skills add mindrally/skills@web-scraping` |\n| **mindrally/skills@scrapy-web-scraping** | 217 | `npx skills add mindrally/skills@scrapy-web-scraping` |\n| **founderjourney/claude-skills@firecrawl** | 28 | `npx skills add founderjourney/claude-skills@firecrawl` |\n\n**推荐理由**：爬取微信公众号、新闻网站必备，journalism版本专为新闻采集优化。\n\n### 3. 搜索能力增强\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **tavily-ai/skills@search** | 4.3K | `npx skills add tavily-ai/skills@search` |\n| **tul-sh/skills@web-search** | 3.3K | `npx skills add tul-sh/skills@web-search` |\n| **supercent-io/skills-template@codebase-search** | 7.4K | `npx skills add supercent-io/skills-template@codebase-search` |\n\n**推荐理由**：Tavily搜索是AI优化的搜索API，返回结构化结果，非常适合情报收集。\n\n---\n\n## 二、专业领域技能\n\n### 1. 市场研究与竞品分析\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **apify/agent-skills@apify-market-research** | 1.5K | `npx skills add apify/agent-skills@apify-market-research` |\n| **apify/agent-skills@apify-competitor-intelligence** | 1.2K | `npx skills add apify/agent-skills@apify-competitor-intelligence` |\n| **davila7/claude-code-templates@market-research-reports** | 547 | `npx skills add davila7/claude-code-templates@market-research-reports` |\n| **anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins@competitive-intelligence** | 161 | `npx skills add anthropics/knowledge-work-plugins@competitive-intelligence` |\n\n**推荐理由**：市场研究和竞品分析专用，与你的核心职责高度匹配。\n\n### 2. 新闻采集与内容策划\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **tul-sh/skills@newsletter-curation** | 1.7K | `npx skills add tul-sh/skills@newsletter-curation` |\n| **cclank/news-aggregator-skill@news-aggregator-skill** | 1.2K | `npx skills add cclank/news-aggregator-skill/news-aggregator-skill` |\n| **yyh211/claude-meta-skill@daily-ai-news** | 642 | `npx skills add yyh211/claude-meta-skill/daily-ai-news` |\n| **sickn33/antigravity-awesome-skills@daily-news-report** | 347 | `npx skills add sickn33/antigravity-awesome-skills/daily-news-report` |\n\n**推荐理由**：每日AI新闻采集、通讯策划，与你的日报任务完美契合。\n\n### 3. 内容研究与写作\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **composiohq/awesome-claude-skills@content-research-writer** | 1.6K | `npx skills add composiohq/awesome-claude-skills/content-research-writer` |\n\n**推荐理由**：内容研究+写作一体化，提升简报生成质量。\n\n---\n\n## 三、数据分析技能\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **supercent-io/skills-template@data-analysis** | 7.8K | `npx skills add supercent-io/skills-template@data-analysis` |\n| **davila7/claude-code-templates@exploratory-data-analysis** | 519 | `npx skills add davila7/claude-code-templates/exploratory-data-analysis` |\n| **github/awesome-copilot@datanalysis-credit-risk** | 2.6K | `npx skills add github/awesome-copilot/datanalysis-credit-risk` |\n\n**推荐理由**：数据分析能力，用于整理爬取的数据、生成分析报告。\n\n---\n\n## 四、自动化技能\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **tul-sh/skills@twitter-automation** | 24.8K | `npx skills add tul-sh/skills@twitter-automation` |\n| **supercent-io/skills-template@workflow-automation** | 7.6K | `npx skills add supercent-io/skills-template/workflow-automation` |\n| **aaaaqwq/claude-code-skills@web-scraping-automation** | 128 | `npx skills add aaaaqwq/claude-code-skills/web-scraping-automation` |\n\n**推荐理由**：自动化工作流，定时爬取、自动整理。\n\n---\n\n## 五、监控能力\n\n| 技能名称 | 安装量 | 安装命令 |\n|---------|--------|----------|\n| **apify/agent-skills@apify-brand-reputation-monitoring** | 1.1K | `npx skills add apify/agent-skills/apify-brand-reputation-monitoring` |\n| **supercent-io/skills-template@monitoring-observability** | 7.3K | `npx skills add supercent-io/skills-template/monitoring-observability` |\n\n**推荐理由**：品牌声誉监控、趋势监控，追踪竞品动态。\n\n---\n\n## 六、推荐安装优先级\n\n### 第一批（核心能力）\n\n```bash\n# 深度研究\nnpx skills add tavily-ai/skills@research -g -y\n\n# 网页爬取\nnpx skills add jamditis/claude-skills-journalism@web-scraping -g -y\n\n# 搜索增强\nnpx skills add tavily-ai/skills@search -g -y\n```\n\n### 第二批（专业能力）\n\n```bash\n# 市场研究\nnpx skills add apify/agent-skills@apify-market-research -g -y\n\n# 竞品分析\nnpx skills add apify/agent-skills@apify-competitor-intelligence -g -y\n\n# 新闻采集\nnpx skills add tul-sh/skills@newsletter-curation -g -y\n```\n\n### 第三批（增强能力）\n\n```bash\n# 数据分析\nnpx skills add supercent-io/skills-template@data-analysis -g -y\n\n# 自动化\nnpx skills add supercent-io/skills-template@workflow-automation -g -y\n\n# AI新闻\nnpx skills add yyh211/claude-meta-skill@daily-ai-news -g -y\n```\n\n---\n\n## 七、技能详情链接\n\n- [Tavily Research](https://skills.sh/tavily-ai/skills/research)\n- [Web Scraping](https://skills.sh/jamditis/claude-skills-journalism/web-scraping)\n- [Market Research](https://skills.sh/apify/agent-skills/apify-market-research)\n- [Competitor Intelligence](https://skills.sh/apify/agent-skills/apify-competitor-intelligence)\n- [Newsletter Curation](https://skills.sh/tul-sh/skills/newsletter-curation)\n- [Deep Research](https://skills.sh/199-biotechnologies/claude-deep-research-skill/deep-research)\n\n---\n\n*搜索工具：npx skills find*\n*来源：https://skills.sh/*","file_path":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-researcher/memory/2026-03-06-技能推荐清单.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2064,"output":2201,"cacheRead":115135,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119400,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772759447305}}
