{"type":"message","id":"1f885282","parentId":"38c5b099","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:24:59.398Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来网络超时问题导致安装失败。但是用户已经有一些技能了。让我查看一下用户现有的技能，并且查看tavily搜索技能（这是我们已有的）的SKILL.md来了解如何使用。\n\n同时，让我检查一下我们已有的tavily搜索技能，它可能就是tavily-ai/skills的一部分。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"网络超时导致安装失败。让我检查你现有的技能，并了解如何更好地使用它们："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-37d43e670bfa4190bc2d693638f5ee5a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-researcher/skills/tavily-search/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-4ab0cbaebc1b423e8b6edfe758fe641c","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-researcher/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":553,"output":214,"cacheRead":142015,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772760285586}}
{"type":"message","id":"2039d70e","parentId":"1f885282","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:24:59.414Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-37d43e670bfa4190bc2d693638f5ee5a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: tavily\ndescription: AI-optimized web search via Tavily API. Returns concise, relevant results for AI agents.\nhomepage: https://tavily.com\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"🔍\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"node\"],\"env\":[\"TAVILY_API_KEY\"]},\"primaryEnv\":\"TAVILY_API_KEY\"}}\n---\n\n# Tavily Search\n\nAI-optimized web search using Tavily API. Designed for AI agents - returns clean, relevant content.\n\n## Search\n\n```bash\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\"\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" -n 10\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --deep\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --topic news\n```\n\n## Options\n\n- `-n <count>`: Number of results (default: 5, max: 20)\n- `--deep`: Use advanced search for deeper research (slower, more comprehensive)\n- `--topic <topic>`: Search topic - `general` (default) or `news`\n- `--days <n>`: For news topic, limit to last n days\n\n## Extract content from URL\n\n```bash\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/extract.mjs \"https://example.com/article\"\n```\n\nNotes:\n- Needs `TAVILY_API_KEY` from https://tavily.com\n- Tavily is optimized for AI - returns clean, relevant snippets\n- Use `--deep` for complex research questions\n- Use `--topic news` for current events\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772760299411}}
{"type":"message","id":"ea7f2896","parentId":"2039d70e","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:24:59.423Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-4ab0cbaebc1b423e8b6edfe758fe641c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `site:` | `site:github.com python` | Search within site |\n| `filetype:` | `filetype:pdf report` | Specific file type |\n| `\"\"` | `\"machine learning\"` | Exact match |\n| `-` | `python -snake` | Exclude term |\n| `OR` | `cat OR dog` | Either term |\n\n## Time Filters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `tbs=qdr:h` | Past hour |\n| `tbs=qdr:d` | Past day |\n| `tbs=qdr:w` | Past week |\n| `tbs=qdr:m` | Past month |\n| `tbs=qdr:y` | Past year |\n\n## Privacy Engines\n\n- **DuckDuckGo**: No tracking\n- **Startpage**: Google results + privacy\n- **Brave**: Independent index\n- **Qwant**: EU GDPR compliant\n\n## Bangs Shortcuts (DuckDuckGo)\n\n| Bang | Destination |\n|------|-------------|\n| `!g` | Google |\n| `!gh` | GitHub |\n| `!so` | Stack Overflow |\n| `!w` | Wikipedia |\n| `!yt` | YouTube |\n\n## WolframAlpha Queries\n\n- Math: `integrate x^2 dx`\n- Conversion: `100 USD to CNY`\n- Stocks: `AAPL stock`\n- Weather: `weather in Beijing`\n\n## Documentation\n\n- `references/advanced-search.md` - Domestic search guide\n- `references/international-search.md` - International search guide\n- `CHANGELOG.md` - Version history\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772760299418}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b042bc5","parentId":"ea7f2896","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:26:06.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我了解了用户已有的技能。用户已经有tavily-search和multi-search-engine这两个核心技能。\n\n由于网络问题，从ClawHub安装新技能失败了。让我：\n1. 总结现有的技能\n2. 说明如何更好地使用这些技能来进行AI技术调研\n3. 提供实用的使用建议\n\n用户关注的是AI技术领域，注重产品技术实现和技术赋能，所以我需要重点从这些角度给出使用建议。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"网络超时导致安装失败。不过你**已经有一些核心技能**了，我来帮你梳理现有能力并提供使用建议：\n\n---\n\n## 📊 你现有的技能清单\n\n| 技能 | 用途 | 是否需要API Key |\n|------|------|----------------|\n| **tavily-search** | AI优化搜索，返回精简结果 | ✅ 需要 TAVILY_API_KEY |\n| **multi-search-engine** | 17个搜索引擎，无API Key | ❌ 不需要 |\n| **github** | GitHub交互（issue、PR、CI） | ✅ 需要 GitHub Token |\n| **self-improving-agent** | 自我学习与改进 | ❌ 不需要 |\n| **proactive-agent** | 主动发现与任务执行 | ❌ 不需要 |\n| **automation-workflows** | 自动化工作流设计 | ❌ 不需要 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 针对你关注领域的使用指南\n\n### 1. AI技术调研（大模型、Agent、技术实现）\n\n**使用 tavily-search 的 deep 模式**：\n\n```bash\n# 深度调研模式，适合技术研究\nnode ~/.openclaw/workspace-researcher/skills/tavily-search/scripts/search.mjs \"GLM-5 智能体架构 技术实现\" --deep -n 10\n\n# 新闻模式，获取最新动态\nnode ~/.openclaw/workspace-researcher/skills/tavily-search/scripts/search.mjs \"AI Agent 最新技术\" --topic news --days 7 -n 10\n```\n\n**使用 multi-search-engine 技术细节搜索**：\n\n```bash\n# 技术文档搜索\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:arxiv.org+transformer+attention+mechanism\"})\n\n# GitHub代码实现\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+RAG+implementation+python\"})\n\n# 技术博客搜索\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:medium.com+LLM+fine+tuning+techniques&tbs=qdr:m\"})\n```\n\n### 2. 产品技术实现调研\n\n**技术架构搜索**：\n\n```bash\n# 产品技术架构\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=AI产品+技术架构+实现方案+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n# 技术选型对比\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=vector+database+comparison+pinecone+weaviate+chroma\"})\n```\n\n### 3. 技术赋能场景挖掘\n\n**行业应用搜索**：\n\n```bash\n# AI+行业应用\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=AI+医疗+金融+教育+应用场景+技术实现\"})\n\n# 技术白皮书\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=AI+赋能+技术白皮书+filetype:pdf&tbs=qdr:y\"})\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💡 针对你的工作流优化建议\n\n### 场景1：深度技术调研\n\n```\n目标：研究 GLM-5 智能体技术实现\n\n步骤：\n1. 用 tavily --deep 搜索技术原理\n2. 用 multi-search 搜索 GitHub 代码实现\n3. 用 web_fetch 抓取论文/技术文档\n4. 整理成技术报告存入 memory/\n```\n\n### 场景2：产品技术分析\n\n```\n目标：分析竞品产品的技术架构\n\n步骤：\n1. 搜索产品名称 + \"技术架构\" + \"实现\"\n2. 搜索产品名称 + \"开源\" + \"GitHub\"\n3. 搜索产品名称 + \"技术分享\" + \"PPT\"\n4. 分析技术栈、架构设计、创新点\n```\n\n### 场景3：技术赋能场景发现\n\n```\n目标：发现AI技术在具体场景的应用\n\n步骤：\n1. 搜索 \"AI + 行业 + 案例 + 技术实现\"\n2. 搜索 \"大模型 + 应用场景 + 落地\"\n3. 搜索 \"Agent + workflow + automation\"\n4. 整理可复用的技术方案\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 建议你补充的技能（等网络恢复后安装）\n\n由于网络问题，以下技能暂时无法安装，建议稍后重试：\n\n```bash\n# 市场研究专用\nnpx skills add apify/agent-skills@apify-market-research -g -y\n\n# 竞品分析专用\nnpx skills add apify/agent-skills@apify-competitor-intelligence -g -y\n\n# 深度研究（增强版）\nnpx skills add tavily-ai/skills@research -g -y\n\n# 新闻爬取\nnpx skills add jamditis/claude-skills-journalism@web-scraping -g -y\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📌 立即可用的技能组合\n\n| 任务 | 推荐技能组合 |\n|------|-------------|\n| 每日AI热点爬取 | multi-search-engine + web_fetch |\n| 深度技术研究 | tavily-search --deep + GitHub搜索 |\n| 产品技术分析 | multi-search-engine + web_fetch |\n| 竞品动态追踪 | tavily-search --topic news |\n\n---\n\n你想让我用现有技能帮你做一次具体的技术调研练习吗？比如搜索某个具体的技术实现方案？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1573,"output":1341,"cacheRead":142463,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145377,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772760299424}}
{"type":"message","id":"224fd4b0","parentId":"0b042bc5","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:53:14.759Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-03-06 09:53 GMT+8] 我现在网络已经恢复了 我需要你每次的研究都需要深入，深入到有开源源码的还需要研究代码的技术说明 另外相比于广度研究 我想你能够深入的研究。每天哪怕发现一两个点都是好的。重点看文章细节，几个文章可以对比去看 抓取到共性都在讨论的点 这个点可能就是核心点。你可以挖掘出来。 每天都需要你去做的就是每日AI热点爬取（抓到横向都在讨论的热点）+深度技术研究+产品技术分析+竞品动态追踪"}],"timestamp":1772761994752}}
{"type":"message","id":"c074d79e","parentId":"224fd4b0","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:53:40.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我改进研究方式：\n1. 深入研究，不要广度，要深度\n2. 有开源源码的要研究代码\n3. 每天发现一两个核心点就够了\n4. 重点看文章细节，对比多篇找共性\n5. 找到大家都在讨论的核心点\n\n现在网络恢复了，我需要重新安装技能，然后按照新的研究方式来工作。\n\n首先安装技能，然后做一个深入研究的示范。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！你的要求非常清晰：\n\n1. **深度 > 广度** - 每天深挖1-2个核心点\n2. **有源码的要研究代码** - 技术实现细节\n3. **多文章对比** - 找共性，识别核心讨论点\n4. **抓取文章正文** - 不只是标题和摘要\n\n让我先安装技能，然后做一个深入研究示范："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-175696a9a0f247e6a602451279b3dcd1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npx skills add tavily-ai/skills@research -g -y","timeout":120000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":144359,"output":313,"cacheRead":1151,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145823,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772761994757}}
