{"type":"message","id":"b0fd8a16","parentId":"bf32efa0","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:58:20.129Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-03-06 09:58 GMT+8] 你现在给到的建议你补充的技能也不是openclaw里的技能 你需要看clawhub上有哪些技能 你现在给到的是claudecode的技能哈。 你需要记住：我现在网络已经恢复了 我需要你每次的研究都需要深入，深入到有开源源码的还需要研究代码的技术说明 另外相比于广度研究 我想你能够深入的研究。每天哪怕发现一两个点都是好的。重点看文章细节，几个文章可以对比去看 抓取到共性都在讨论的点 这个点可能就是核心点。你可以挖掘出来。 每天都需要你去做的就是每日AI热点爬取（抓到横向都在讨论的热点）+深度技术研究+产品技术分析+竞品动态追踪"}],"timestamp":1772762300122}}
{"type":"message","id":"d819008f","parentId":"b0fd8a16","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:58:49.092Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户纠正了我几个关键点：\n\n1. 我之前推荐的技能是claude code的技能，不是openclaw的技能。我需要看clawhub上的技能。\n\n2. 用户强调：\n   - 网络已恢复\n   - 每次研究需要深入，有开源源码的要研究代码技术说明\n   - 深度 > 广度，每天发现1-2个点就好\n   - 重点看文章细节，多文章对比，找共性讨论点（这些点就是核心点）\n\n3. 用户的工作流需求：\n   - 每日AI热点爬取（横向都在讨论的热点）\n   - 深度技术研究\n   - 产品技术分析\n   - 竞品动态追踪\n\n让我先检查一下之前的research技能安装情况，然后：\n1. 使用clawhub CLI查找适合的技能\n2. 安装clawhub上的技能（不是skills.sh的）\n3. 执行深入研究示范\n\n我需要先理解clawhub的CLI使用方式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白！让我先检查 clawhub CLI，然后搜索适合深度研究的技能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e534369ff5cb4c7ca8649cc1b5fb952e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub --help"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-eb0bd1d60a8a4b5b905b33c8826b9299","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":146222,"output":477,"cacheRead":1151,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147850,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772762300127}}
{"type":"message","id":"2366f325","parentId":"d819008f","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:58:49.695Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-e534369ff5cb4c7ca8649cc1b5fb952e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage: clawhub [options] [command]\n\nClawHub CLI v0.7.0\ninstall, update, search, and publish agent skills.\n\nOptions:\n  -V, --cli-version                       Show CLI version\n  --workdir <dir>                         Working directory (default: cwd)\n  --dir <dir>                             Skills directory (relative to workdir, default: skills)\n  --site <url>                            Site base URL (for browser login)\n  --registry <url>                        Registry API base URL\n  --no-input                              Disable prompts\n  -h, --help                              display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  login [options]                         Log in (opens browser or stores token)\n  logout                                  Remove stored token\n  whoami                                  Validate token\n  auth                                    Authentication commands\n  search [options] <query...>             Vector search skills\n  install [options] <slug>                Install into <dir>/<slug>\n  update [options] [slug]                 Update installed skills\n  uninstall [options] <slug>              Uninstall a skill\n  list                                    List installed skills (from lockfile)\n  explore [options]                       Browse latest updated skills from the registry\n  inspect [options] <slug>                Fetch skill metadata and files without installing\n  publish [options] <path>                Publish skill from folder\n  delete [options] <slug>                 Soft-delete a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  hide [options] <slug>                   Hide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  undelete [options] <slug>               Restore a hidden skill (moderator/admin only)\n  unhide [options] <slug>                 Unhide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  ban-user [options] <handleOrId>         Ban a user and delete owned skills (moderator/admin only)\n  set-role [options] <handleOrId> <role>  Change a user role (admin only)\n  star [options] <slug>                   Add a skill to your highlights\n  unstar [options] <slug>                 Remove a skill from your highlights\n  sync [options]                          Scan local skills and publish new/updated ones\n\nEnv:\n  CLAWHUB_SITE\n  CLAWHUB_REGISTRY\n  CLAWHUB_WORKDIR\n  (CLAWDHUB_* supported)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":569,"aggregated":"Usage: clawhub [options] [command]\n\nClawHub CLI v0.7.0\ninstall, update, search, and publish agent skills.\n\nOptions:\n  -V, --cli-version                       Show CLI version\n  --workdir <dir>                         Working directory (default: cwd)\n  --dir <dir>                             Skills directory (relative to workdir, default: skills)\n  --site <url>                            Site base URL (for browser login)\n  --registry <url>                        Registry API base URL\n  --no-input                              Disable prompts\n  -h, --help                              display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  login [options]                         Log in (opens browser or stores token)\n  logout                                  Remove stored token\n  whoami                                  Validate token\n  auth                                    Authentication commands\n  search [options] <query...>             Vector search skills\n  install [options] <slug>                Install into <dir>/<slug>\n  update [options] [slug]                 Update installed skills\n  uninstall [options] <slug>              Uninstall a skill\n  list                                    List installed skills (from lockfile)\n  explore [options]                       Browse latest updated skills from the registry\n  inspect [options] <slug>                Fetch skill metadata and files without installing\n  publish [options] <path>                Publish skill from folder\n  delete [options] <slug>                 Soft-delete a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  hide [options] <slug>                   Hide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  undelete [options] <slug>               Restore a hidden skill (moderator/admin only)\n  unhide [options] <slug>                 Unhide a skill (moderator/admin only)\n  ban-user [options] <handleOrId>         Ban a user and delete owned skills (moderator/admin only)\n  set-role [options] <handleOrId> <role>  Change a user role (admin only)\n  star [options] <slug>                   Add a skill to your highlights\n  unstar [options] <slug>                 Remove a skill from your highlights\n  sync [options]                          Scan local skills and publish new/updated ones\n\nEnv:\n  CLAWHUB_SITE\n  CLAWHUB_REGISTRY\n  CLAWHUB_WORKDIR\n  (CLAWDHUB_* supported)","cwd":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-researcher"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772762329692}}
