{"type":"message","id":"1a46ac1b","parentId":"b4e101de","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:59:38.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，找到了clawhub上的技能。让我挑选几个最相关的：\n\n**研究类**：\n- deep-research-pro (3.564)\n- academic-deep-research (3.550)\n- market-research (3.535)\n- in-depth-research (3.509)\n\n**爬取类**：\n- xpr-web-scraping (3.533)\n- afrexai-web-scraping-engine (3.430)\n- web-scraping-api (3.407)\n\n**AI Agent类**：\n- ai-agent-helper (3.686)\n- ai-agent-setup (3.481)\n\n让我安装这些技能，然后查看它们的具体内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-0f66234b12814422a846d98c9c04ece0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub install deep-research-pro"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-43fb81df50114abb8a4a5dbc11af8238","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub install academic-deep-research"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-5ac291b209f44fe7b000cb6905310f4e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub install xpr-web-scraping"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-63b4f1066ec6412786a11bbc2035757e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub install ai-agent-helper"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":797,"output":358,"cacheRead":148095,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149250,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772762359373}}
